Title: AC/DC
Writer: Daniel J. Goor (created by), Michael Schur (created by), Kylie Condon, Gabe Liedman (executive story editor), Lakshmi Sundaram (executive story editor), Matt O'Brien (executive story editor), Brigitte Liebowitz (story editor)

Plot: Jake is badly injured trying to chase a suspect, but he refuses to take time off from the job. Holt and Rosa have a awkward dinner date with their significant others, so they invite Amy and Gina along as well.
